Key Match Events: Fred VanVleet stole the ball late to secure the victory
Anthony Davis had 30 points and 13 rebounds

Miscellaneous Highlights: Amen Thompson added 23 points and a career-high 16 rebounds in his return after a two-game suspension
Others: The Rockets remained up by seven about a minute after that when a 3 by Davis cut the lead to 117-113 before the basket by James
